Company Profile
Luoyang Heavy Machinery Co., Ltd. the former was CITIC Heavy Machinery  Industry and Commerce Co., Ltd. It was used be subsidiary of CITIC Heavy  Machinery Co., Ltd. The company was founded in 1981 and finished joint  stock reform in 2005. There are eight subsidiaries and it's an  independent legal entity with the qualifications of operating import  & export trade.

With a garden-like industrial park and modern standard plant covering  80,000 square meters, CIC HMC possesses advanced equipments,  technologies and detecting methods. After more than 30 years  development, the company has developed into a collectivized one with  product designing, manufacture, installation and technical services as a  whole. The products comprise all the equipments used in mining,  metallurgy, construction materials, mining processing, petrol chemical,  new power generation as well as the related accessories with automatic  control, engineering plastic, high power reducer and large-sized  castings & forgings, etc. Now, CIC HMC is the national major  industry and heavy machinery manufacturing base in the middle of China.

Through focusing on marketing and improving management inside,  optimizing the resource collocation, progress the strategy of science  and technology leading enterprise development, CIC HMC has formed its  own unique product structure and technological superiority. Besides, it  has completed more than 20 major research projects, five of which won  National Science and Technology Progress Award, three got Henan Science  and Technology Progress Award, and more than 20 have national patents.  It has been recognized as the Mining Machinery and Scientific Research  Base by China University of Mining and Technology and the Teaching  Practice Base of Henan Science and Technology University.

CIC HMC has acquired ISO 9001:2008 Certification of conformity of  Management System Certification, Mine Product Safety Authentication,  Recognition for BV Mode Ⅱ Survey Scheme in France, Mining Electrical  Equipment KY Certification, etc.
The company has also acquired "Fully Quality Management Achievement  Award", "Top 50 Enterprises", "Henan Outstanding Innovative Enterprise”  and “The Most Powerful Enterprises of Henan" in 2010.　　
 





CITICMC -The largest mining equipment and cement equipment manufacturers in China.CITICMC is a global supplier of technology and services to customers in the process industries,including Mining,Construction,Metallurgical,Environmental,Power,Chemical,Marine,Casting&Forgings. 

