Company Overview of CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells heavy machinery for the mining and non-ferrous, metallurgical, power, environmental, cement, and chemical industries in China and internationally. The company offers mining equipment components for OEM suppliers, such as grinding mills; vertical stirred mills; gyratory crushers and AJ JAW crushers for the mining and aggregate industries; high pressure grinding rolls; mine hoists; shaft drilling machines; crushing stations for use in open-pit coalmines, as well as in metallurgical, non-ferrous metal, and other semi-continuous mining processes; coal preparation equipment; horizontal rotary furnaces; rotary kilns for alumina; and vertical ...
CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells heavy machinery for the mining and non-ferrous, metallurgical, power, environmental, cement, and chemical industries in China and internationally. The company offers mining equipment components for OEM suppliers, such as grinding mills; vertical stirred mills; gyratory crushers and AJ JAW crushers for the mining and aggregate industries; high pressure grinding rolls; mine hoists; shaft drilling machines; crushing stations for use in open-pit coalmines, as well as in metallurgical, non-ferrous metal, and other semi-continuous mining processes; coal preparation equipment; horizontal rotary furnaces; rotary kilns for alumina; and vertical disk filters. It also provides rotary and mixer furnaces for steel making; large-sized crushers and ball mills for mineral separation; billet casters and slab casters for continuous casting; HP roller mills; lime production equipment; medium-thickness plate, de-coiler, cold continuous, and single-stand cold rolls; hot piercers, cold tube mills, and cold-drawn tube mills; plate, pipe, and bar straighteners, as well as leveler sets; and ized pellet kilns. In addition, the company offers equipment for hydropower stations, power stations, and power generation and low-temperature waste heat generation, as well as bridge cranes; equipment for environmental protection projects; and equipment for cement lines. Further, it provides machinery for paper mills, fertilizer plants, phosphate fertilizer plants, chemical plants, and others; large reducers for use in mining, building material, metallurgical, power and petroleum, chemical industries, etc.; large castings and forgings; and after-market services, such as engineered spares, steel and iron casting foundries, machine shop services, training programs, and maintenance services. The company was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Luoyang, China. CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of CITIC Corporation Limited.
Detailed Description


