CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd. Key Developments

CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Board Meeting, Jul 05, 2017
Jul 5 17
CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Board Meeting, Jul 05, 2017. Agenda: To discuss and approve issues including the proposal of scheme of assets purchase through shares issuance and cash payment and raising supporting funds; to consider the proposal of signing agreement on assets purchase through shares issuance and cash payment; to consider agreement on performance promise and profit compensation' with collateral entry-into-force condition; and to consider the proposal of requesting shareholders' meeting to authorize Directorate to fully handle relevant issues of this transaction.


CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Board Meeting, Jun 16, 2017
Jun 16 17
CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Board Meeting, Jun 16, 2017. Agenda: To discuss and approve the proposal of continuous trading suspension due to assets purchase through shares issuance; and to consider the proposal of applying for comprehensive credit lines to Banks.


CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Annual General Meeting, Jun 29, 2017
Jun 8 17
CITIC Heavy Industries Co., Ltd., Annual General Meeting, Jun 29, 2017, at 09:00 China Standard Time. Agenda: To discuss issues including the annual report of 2016 and its abstract; to consider the scheme of profit distribution for 2016; and to consider the proposal of renewing engagement of auditor for financial reports of 2017.


